				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Nettie and the other druids are forced to drive out the tieflings by force. ADs cover the attack, moving to attack position, and ADs while Nettie's waiting to strike. Nettie doesn't want to kill anyone, and hopes the tieflings will leave until the very end, but will fight if she needs to."
